item.title: EP 42 - My Baby, She Wrote Me A Letter

item.description:
Today we summon succubi and mess with love spells!

Patreon
https://www.patreon.com/user?u=18482113

MERCH STORE!!!

The legends of the succubi and incubi are as old as time itself. Demonic creatures who suck out your life energy while giving you a little tingly touch. But nowadays, some people believe you can summon these demons at will. Anyone down for a little Hex-flix and chill?

Then we look at love spells. Do they work? Can you keep a lover from leaving you? And is there a simple spell that will allow you to know if anyone around you is gay? Probably no to all three, but we talk about them anyways!
